metadata.name: OG Member
metadata.description:
Claimooors of this OG Member token participated in the WILD & FREE community buildings grand opening event on Dec. 8th 2022 at the punk6529 Open Metaverse, Museum District, Alpha Zone and are OG Members of the community. OG Members are eligible for free OG Member token claim after claiming the event POAP. The OG Member token is a multi purpose token and can be used as an object in virtual galleries & will grant access to future token gated events at WILD & FREE OM buildings aswell as other perks in the future.

Lets create our presence in OM together as a diverse community of artists, art collectors & degen without borders and regardless of genre, nationality, religion, race, background, web3 focus area etc.! One web3 community, united and inclusive!!  
Much love, be wild & free always!  
Dom aka wildalps

Big shoutout to the legend 3D artist @DS_art_ for donating this incredible 3D object of wildalps and Skadi for our fam, thank you tons fren!! <3
